com.betabot.script.utils

Class SkillTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betabot.script.utils.SkillTracker
  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class SkillTracker
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for tracking experience gains in specified skills.

    The three arrays (skills, startExp, currentExp) are constantly congruent, and updated as such.
